&lt;p&gt;As we expand our platform capabilities, we are investing in AI-driven features that improve how healthcare organizations interact with their data, workflows, and operational systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;AI Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to help design and implement AI-native capabilities within MedicatOne.&lt;/p&gt;
