&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with product leadership and engineering to architect and deploy AI-powered systems that interact with structured healthcare data and operational workflows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role requires strong technical execution as well as fluency in data analytics and healthcare informatics concepts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a build-and-ship role where you will play a key part in translating AI opportunities into real product functionality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this position, you will help to accelerate engineering performance and drive AI-enabled innovation across Medicat in our workflows and in our SaaS product.&lt;/p&gt;
