&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You will play a critical role in Banyan Software’s sourcing efforts by identifying and engaging vertical market software companies, expanding our market coverage, building relationships with software business owners, and creating opportunities that ultimately lead to acquisitions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
