&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Your efforts will directly contribute to Banyan’s acquisition growth strategy. If you enjoy connecting with business leaders, uncovering opportunities, learning about new industries, and thriving in a performance-driven environment, we want to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
