&lt;div id=&quot;fortidlp-input-element-parent&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CEO - M3 Informatica&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Location: Madrid, Spain&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About M3 Informatica:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;M3 Informática is a Spanish vertical SaaS company delivering HR, payroll, and workforce management software purpose-built for the public sector including healthcare authorities and local government. The company has served its public administration clients for over three decades, operates on a highly recurring subscription model, and holds a strong market position within its vertical. Not a single client has ever churned. M3 is now entering its first chapter of international ownership under Banyan Software, combining three decades of deep regulatory lock-in with the operational and AI expertise of a global software group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will join M3 Informática directly as CEO, reporting to a Banyan Operating Leader with full operational authority over how you run the business. The business has to be durable, the product has to be the primary competitive advantage, and the opportunity to create structural distance through AI is real.&amp;nbsp;You will own the most important client relationships from day one, build the commercial infrastructure from scratch, and partner your CTO to define the platform&#39;s next decade.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial &amp;amp; Revenue Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
