&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools — including Claude and ChatGPT — as core daily instruments. Draft documents, build compliance trackers, summarize diligence materials, generate first-pass resolutions, and automate repetitive workflows using AI. Be the person on the team who pushes the boundaries of what AI-assisted legal work looks like in practice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with legal leadership to identify where manual effort persists and propose technology or workflow solutions. Contribute to the design of Banyan’s legal tech stack as the portfolio continues to grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
