&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and prepare joinder documentation when new entities (including newly acquired portfolio companies) join existing credit facilities, working with external counsel and lenders to ensure all conditions to joinder are satisfied and executed documents are properly filed and tracked.&lt;/li&gt;
