&lt;li&gt;Maintain and develop a roster of overflow counsel across North America who service OpCo day-to-day legal needs, billing the OpCo directly. You train this network on Banyan standards and best practices and serve as the quality control layer across the relationship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage IP matters for the global portfolio through a dedicated external law firm relationship, coordinating filings, renewals, enforcement questions, and strategic IP matters on behalf of portfolio companies&lt;/li&gt;
